snippet.title: Honey, I Joined A Cult - Official Steam Early Access Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Get another look at the simulation game in this latest trailer for Honey, I Joined A Cult.

It's time to start working towards that ultimate goal of enlightenment, faith, and money...lots and lots of money. Create, customize, expand and manage your own cult whilst listening to funky music in Honey, I Joined a Cult, heading to Steam Early Access on September 14, 2021.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #HoneyIJoinedACult
